						>ClearSky Partner Program</span
					>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Main Headlines -->
			<div class="mb-[24px] text-center">
				<h2
					class="mb-4 text-[24px] leading-tight font-semibold "
				>
					The ClearSky Founders Program
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto  text-base leading-tight text-[#1A1A1A] opacity-95">
					Founders gain the advantage of the ClearSky network before competitors in their market.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Content Grid -->
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-[15px] lg:flex-row lg:items-stretch lg:justify-center">
				<!-- Left Column: Program Description -->
				<div
					class="flex-1 rounded-[16px] bg-[#4267AD] p-[24px] shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]"
				>
					<div class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-[10px] border-2 border-white p-[16px]">
						<p class="mb-7 text-[16px] text-white">
							The ClearSky Business Platform helps businesses grow through a connected system of
							discovery, engagement, and intelligent communication.
						</p>
						<p class="mb-7 text-[16px] text-white">
							Rather than launching everywhere at once, ClearSky introduces the platform through a
							limited Founders Program. This approach allows each market to maintain meaningful
							opportunity for participating businesses.
						</p>
						<p class="mb-7 text-[16px] text-white">
							Founders secure their Primary Category within a defined territory, ensuring the
							platform grows without enabling direct local competitors within the same category.
						</p>
						<p class="text-[16px] text-white">
							As Founders begin using the platform, ClearSky continuously <br/> improves workflows,
							automation, and AI-driven insights using real <br/> -world performance data—so the system
							evolves based on what actually works in the field.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>


				<!-- Right Column: Founder Advantages -->
				<div
					class="flex-1 rounded-[16px] bg-[#4267AD] p-[24px] shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]"
				>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
						<h3 class="mb-2 text-[15px] font-semibold text-white">Founder Advantages</h3>

						<!-- Advantage Item 1 -->
						<button
							type="button"
							class="text-left w-full rounded-[10px] border-2 border-white p-5 transition-all duration-300 outline-none hover:border-white hover:bg-white/5 hover:shadow-[1px_3px_10px_3px_#FFFFFFBF] focus:shadow-[1px_3px_10px_3px_#FFFFFFBF]"
						>
							<h4 class="mb-1 text-[17px] font-bold text-white">Founder Pricing</h4>
							<p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.6] text-white/90">
								Receive founder pricing at approximately 50% below comparable module packages. Your
								rate is locked for the first 24 months after activation.
							</p>
						</button>

						<!-- Advantage Item 2 -->
						<button
							type="button"
							class="text-left w-full relative z-10 rounded-[10px] border-2 border-white p-5 transition-all duration-300 outline-none hover:border-white hover:bg-white/5 hover:shadow-[1px_3px_10px_3px_#FFFFFFBF] focus:shadow-[1px_3px_10px_3px_#FFFFFFBF]"
						>
							<h4 class="mb-1 text-[17px] font-bold text-white">Market Exclusivity</h4>
							<p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.6] text-white">
								Secure your Primary Category within your territory under strict licensing limits
								designed to protect market opportunity.
							</p>
						</button>

						<!-- Advantage Item 3 -->
						<button
							type="button"
							class="text-left w-full rounded-[10px] border-2 border-white p-5 transition-all duration-300 outline-none hover:border-white hover:bg-white/5 hover:shadow-[1px_3px_10px_3px_#FFFFFFBF] focus:shadow-[1px_3px_10px_3px_#FFFFFFBF]"
						>
							<h4 class="mb-1 text-[17px] font-bold text-white">Direct Feedback Loop</h4>
							<p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.6] text-white/90">
								Founders help shape the platform. Real-world performance data improves workflows,
								automation, and AI recommendations.
							</p>
						</button>

						<!-- Advantage Item 4 -->
						<button
							type="button"
							class="text-left w-full rounded-[10px] border-2 border-white p-5 transition-all duration-300 outline-none hover:border-white hover:bg-white/5 hover:shadow-[1px_3px_10px_3px_#FFFFFFBF] focus:shadow-[1px_3px_10px_3px_#FFFFFFBF]"
						>
							<h4 class="mb-1 text-[17px] font-bold text-white">Compounding System</h4>
